{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"092f83977a","title":"陈伯达江青给北京航空学院“红旗”的电话指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b478681fe0","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":26,"articleId":"092f83977a","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"夺权和一月革命","id":"714adabb18","type":"主题"},{"name":"吴德","id":"7f0393737e","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2e4f8d586b","type":"title","text":"陈伯达江青给北京航空学院“红旗”的电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"092f83977a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"575111a0da","type":"paragraph","text":"起草一个决定，不必开誓师大会，考虑准备北京市工农兵和革命师生代表会，组织市人民政府，不一定用市长这一形式，标语和传单暂不印，转告（其它组织）。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"092f83977a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e5c87a0cf","type":"paragraph","text":"工农兵都派代表参加。那一些可以接管，用什么形式，应经代表会研究。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"092f83977a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a09f79c7df","type":"paragraph","text":"立即放吴德同志回去，监督其工作，代表会马上准备工农兵代表会，代表会不能交给这一派，也不能交给那一派。北京市学生多比例可多一些，可搞主任，轮流主持会议。接管问题，可在会上充分讨论。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"092f83977a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"56fa996de8","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志传达主席一句话：凡是搞宗派主义，小团体主义，最后都搞不成的，把这个精神传给其它组织。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"092f83977a","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}